<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">專業手機維修<br /><span class="hero-highlight">深水埗即到即修</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        螢幕爆裂、鏡頭損壞、電池老化？MonCity 為你提供快捷可靠嘅手機維修服務。
        深水埗站 D2 出口，步行即達。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://wa.me/85269960711" class="btn btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          💬 WhatsApp 即時查詢
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+85269960711" class="btn btn-outline">
          📞 6996 0711
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <span>✅ 即日維修</span>
        <span>✅ 專業技師</span>
        <span>✅ 原廠物料</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light) 0%, var(--paper) 100%);
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
  }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 800px; }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero-highlight { color: var(--primary); }
  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 48px 0 40px; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
    .hero-actions .btn { text-align: center; justify-content: center; }
    .hero-trust { gap: 12px; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  }
</style>
